      "date": "2013-04-08 20:23:35.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/4eadd3a6-a087-11e2-898f-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  No failures.",
